{"tid":1808363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲以為一百萬出返黎係好開始，點知成個熱門咁多嗌交割𥱊post，手足俾狗拉唔知會受咩對待都可以拎出黎笑......","createTime":"2020-01-02T10:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T12:58:19.000Z","uid":31215,"like":60,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"cc9c34af984451301d21601d5fccca036d82d81a","tid":1808363,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:16:29.000Z","msg":"手足有咩未做得好咪互相提點囉<br />\n大家都係摸住石頭過河<br />\n又唔係聖人<br />\n總有野未如理想<br />\n樣樣做得準確根本冇可能<br />\n使唔使恥笑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾狗拉可能會俾狗性侵同打<br />\n<br />\n仲有不滿pepe頭<br />\n人地都係民陣和理非主場先出黎，係BB車大肚婆都出黎行嘅日子，咁都要睇唔過眼<br />\n人地上左幾多報紙<br />\n各有各做，做乜反對人地做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非唔反燒獅子<br />\n勇武都唔使反pepe頭<br />\n<br />\n話人屌狗=出賣勇武更加唔成立<br />\n咁多次和你shop屌狗<br />\n都係街坊第一排屌<br />\n師奶阿叔屌得最大聲<br />\n一有咩動靜<br />\n個個嗌有文具快啲走<br />\n我戴住頂帽都叫我走後啲<br />\n街坊幾時出賣勇武<br />\n<br />\n仲有捉鬼<br />\n呢個係做錯左<br />\n但之後咪修正返囉<br />\n出多啲文宣解釋捉鬼禍害囉<br />\n黑警出咁多喬裝<br />\n就係引你地自己捉鬼<br />\n然後啲文宣唔好淨係貼連登<br />\n一陣啲冇跟得咁貼嘅人<br />\n中黑警局走去捉鬼<br />\n跟住又話心灰又話想quit <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59c9be1c5b21a528815a6a0151e039d29168f2c4","tid":1808363,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7fcd8a334ed448dc4c35cc09632bdc277c2bff","tid":1808363,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"連登係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef5fe8d8185f6bf38795c951edbe58fa4dba43d","tid":1808363,"uid":41850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋要多啲人睇到<br />\n<br />\n仲有其實次次遊行之後都千祈唔好上連登，<br />\n因為肯定會一班人咁講，無謂令到自己唔開心"},{"pid":"ecb31f2147954c5ad9306310c0f20e9f26507e4c","tid":1808363,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082bf71ad9ae9f12af4770d09a87754d57faf2c6","tid":1808363,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:26:01.000Z","msg":"連登一早被嚴格滲透"},{"pid":"3a8e8c1ad26df5c9207d0a689b875a74b1fbc1a2","tid":1808363,"uid":33381,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"上少啲連登個人開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔覺頭套有咩問題 和理非遊行想出分力姐<br />\n又唔係打緊仗咁樣就冇所謂"},{"pid":"8c7a89b12cbd6fe061a142aac0ecc1d149e419ee","tid":1808363,"uid":105405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:27:46.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n記住不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰<br />\n我地都係咁先可以一路走來"},{"pid":"c2d165998583ded3b102e28530c01aaba124eb57","tid":1808363,"uid":31215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3ef5fe8d8185f6bf38795c951edbe58fa4dba43d","tid":1808363,"uid":41850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:24:29.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋要多啲人睇到<br />\n<br />\n仲有其實次次遊行之後都千祈唔好上連登，<br />\n因為肯定會一班人咁講，無謂令到自己唔開心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:29:48.000Z","msg":"有班人成日屌和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非其實已經好幫手<br />\n<br />\n大家記唔記得<br />\n救理大嗰晚<br />\n和理非冇gear<br />\n催淚彈捱完一波又一波<br />\n叫住入poly 救學生就行上去<br />\n師奶都做人鏈傳磚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d658331586e3926f6b44b14ece014d4855578a9c","tid":1808363,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a8e8c1ad26df5c9207d0a689b875a74b1fbc1a2","tid":1808363,"uid":33381,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T1