:42.000Z","msg":"上少啲連登個人開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔覺頭套有咩問題 和理非遊行想出分力姐<br />\n又唔係打緊仗咁樣就冇所謂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:33:46.000Z","msg":"啱，落場先會發現連登仔先係左膠"},{"pid":"31e14487c19bfbf3cc89d0f64eb93a02c8948f20","tid":1808363,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:33:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d38360456601bff65489bb09176d12ad719a0b9","tid":1808363,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24828d31708fa7d0d32071db71c33c376231995c","tid":1808363,"uid":128603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:31:28.000Z","msg":"真實係啲熱毛帶風向，搞分化"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:34:00.000Z","msg":"大家自己要有獨立思考<br />\n唔好見人屌左膠就屌埋一份<br />\n各有各做<br />\n左膠包容到勇武<br />\n勇武都唔阻人玩頭套同行為藝術<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ed02a8b2b48c2b9540472c2f17d874c65742ae","tid":1808363,"uid":141097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91c23e7190a9e8a4d47c407c389a97c5ce54767","tid":1808363,"uid":249703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:34:19.000Z","msg":"睇少啲連登就得<br />\n根本現場氣氛完全唔同"},{"pid":"091354574d7b671746a1f83366f561b316f8b84d","tid":1808363,"uid":73089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:34:21.000Z","msg":"提咩點 一提就分化撚 割蓆撚 講經咩"},{"pid":"c82e25c55f02a72b6b3c6961c29aa477c1318ead","tid":1808363,"uid":177150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:34:45.000Z","msg":"全部我都好贊成，屌親果啲係分化狗"},{"pid":"c6d55c98ac17fc885e9592ae317f74bab341094d","tid":1808363,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:36:16.000Z","msg":"成班分化扮勇武，割和理非<br />\n和理非要人帶領，要教育佢地，狂屌做乜"},{"pid":"ad4b346d2bb0f3d3c512490d9503627c238ed69d","tid":1808363,"uid":120990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit