\n你係咪好高興先?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:57:19.000Z","msg":"呢個問題你問返同黑警影相既人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f48787dc837e4d5430cbdfbe4635552687232fc","tid":1808363,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc9c34af984451301d21601d5fccca036d82d81a","tid":1808363,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:16:29.000Z","msg":"手足有咩未做得好咪互相提點囉<br />\n大家都係摸住石頭過河<br />\n又唔係聖人<br />\n總有野未如理想<br />\n樣樣做得準確根本冇可能<br />\n使唔使恥笑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾狗拉可能會俾狗性侵同打<br />\n<br />\n仲有不滿pepe頭<br />\n人地都係民陣和理非主場先出黎，係BB車大肚婆都出黎行嘅日子，咁都要睇唔過眼<br />\n人地上左幾多報紙<br />\n各有各做，做乜反對人地做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非唔反燒獅子<br />\n勇武都唔使反pepe頭<br />\n<br />\n話人屌狗=出賣勇武更加唔成立<br />\n咁多次和你shop屌狗<br />\n都係街坊第一排屌<br />\n師奶阿叔屌得最大聲<br />\n一有咩動靜<br />\n個個嗌有文具快啲走<br />\n我戴住頂帽都叫我走後啲<br />\n街坊幾時出賣勇武<br />\n<br />\n仲有捉鬼<br />\n呢個係做錯左<br />\n但之後咪修正返囉<br />\n出多啲文宣解釋捉鬼禍害囉<br />\n黑警出咁多喬裝<br />\n就係引你地自己捉鬼<br />\n然後啲文宣唔好淨係貼連登<br />\n一陣啲冇跟得咁貼嘅人<br />\n中黑警局走去捉鬼<br />\n跟住又話心灰又話想quit <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:59:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[元旦遊行因為裝修所以停？]</span><br />\n聽完真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無裝修警甴就無理由停？你聽下四點狗辯會先啦，咁撚多歪理，佢要停你大把濕鳩理由啦<br />\n<br />\n而且我想講全港得返黃絲守法咋，你地咪繼續跟住規則玩囉<br />\n<br />\n你地見唔到休班狗犯法點判咩？<br />\n見唔到的士撞完手足無事有錢收咩？<br />\n見唔到琴日有的士撞人今日都無人拉佢咩？<br />\n見唔到陳彥霖祼屍無可疑咩？<br />\n見唔到周梓樂被跳樓無人查咩？<br />\n<br />\n你地繼續囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae9dda08470db15cc026a4bece2b55a9956486b8","tid":1808363,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:03:32.000Z","msg":"中共全力分化緊"},{"pid":"7087d196aa97627bd9da90920ef774b3dd486e67","tid":1808363,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae7fcd8a334ed448dc4c35cc09632bdc277c2bff","tid":1808363,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:23:45.000Z","msg":"連登係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:19:16.000Z","msg":"同現場係兩個世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"593918fac01f232a615195497609082098fdbd7c","tid":1808363,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae9dda08470db15cc026a4bece2b55a9956486b8","tid":1808363,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:03:32.000Z","msg":"中共全力分化緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:37:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde5062dd882d32276682bd0a03a1c8ddde60e31","tid":1808363,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ce71727cc02618cddf5eb97f9e8318ba928d465","tid":1808363,"uid":319380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:43:11.000Z","msg":"次次大遊行前後2日都會係咁<br />\n<br />\n好快又無事架喇<br />\n過左7個月，仲有過百萬人出嚟<br />\n你就知大家就算點互鬧，到最後都會和解<br />\n要對手足有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日超多老人家同小朋友出嚟支持年輕人<br />\n要多謝佢哋呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}